name: KILLUA TROOPS MK2 <<WINTER>>
description:
EGO NAME: WINTER
YEAR OF RESURRECTION: 3021 BC
BATTALION: ELDER

WINTER is the second killua troop to rise up as an enemy target kidnapper in the xerces war. moving fast rumbling like a blizzard disrupting the war situation and making it easier for him to kidnap targets for the benefit of prisoners and interrogations. chaos is a very favorable situation for WINTER.
